          "name": "damage",
          "params": {
            "magnitude": 2500,
            "element": "fire"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "lifesteal",
          "params": {
            "percent": 0.08
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "Charcoal lines leap between targets as if a cartographer's hand redraws the battlefield in scorched arcs, each stroke consuming what it maps. The tower's wind carries the residue outward, and the surveyor breathes back what the fire takes."
    }
